query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi.info in ('Kyrgyz','Arabic','Gujarati','Estonian','Slovak','Afrikaans','Urdu','Romanian','Tagalog','Bosnian','Hungarian') AND cct2.kind not in ('complete','crew','cast') AND it2.info not in ('essays','sound mix','LD aspect ratio','LD language','magazine cover photo','languages','production process protocol','top 250 rank','gross','soundtrack','countries') AND cct1.kind in ('cast','crew') AND n.name not like '%Q%' AND n.name not like '%c%' AND n.gender in ('m') AND it1.info in ('opening weekend','admissions') AND t.production_year > 1991 AND (t.title like '%knife%' OR t.title like '%letter%' OR t.title like '%hammer%' OR t.title like '%road%')
